	{{#collectible.custom}}
		<p>When you are adding parts please try and add existing parts whenever possible.  If you do have to add a new part to the system and you purhaseed it from someone please add it as a <strong>new collectible</strong>, attaching that new part to the collectible.  Once it is approved you can add the existing part to your custom.</p>
		<p>You will only be able to add new custom or commissioned parts directly to this collectible. These parts will not be able to be shared.</p>
	{{/collectible.custom}}
	{{#collectible.original}}
		<p>Since this is an original collectible, new parts added to this collectible will not be able to be shared.</p>
	{{/collectible.original}}
